<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="60" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1959,2020]" pageId="1" pageNumber="60">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,1959,1984]" pageId="1" pageNumber="60">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Epandrial lobe long, thin; surstylus nearly straight, distinctly thickened basally. Fore coxa and all femora dark brownish yellow. All femora with distinct av basally.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
